    {
      "suggestedId": "emilkowalski-frequency-appropriate-match-motion-to-how",
      "source": "emilkowalski",
      "text": "Frequency-appropriate. Match motion to how often it's seen. Keyboard-initiated and 100+/day actions get no animation. Tens/day gets reduced motion. Occasional gets standard. Rare/first-time can have delight.",
      "category": "animations",
      "tags": [
        "motion",
